snippet: Rookie Jorge Soler had a two-run double to become the second player in Cubs history with as many as 10 RBIs in his first seven games as Chicago beat Milwaukee 6-2 on Wednesday night....

headline.print_headline: Soler Drives in Two More Runs as Cubs Beat Brewers
headline.main: Soler Drives in Two More Runs as Cubs Beat Brewers

lead_paragraph: Rookie Jorge Soler had a two-run double to become the second player in Cubs history with as many as 10 RBIs in his first seven games as Chicago beat Milwaukee 6-2 on Wednesday night.
